sequenceDiagram
    participant GUI as Qt UI
    participant API as REST API
    participant Gate as GatewayCore
    participant Dev as DeviceSim

    GUI->>API: POST /start
    API->>Gate: start_device()
    Gate->>Dev: start()
    Dev-->>Gate: state = Measuring

    GUI->>API: POST /stop
    API->>Gate: stop_device()
    Gate->>Dev: stop()
    Dev-->>Gate: state = Idle